# Visual Modules Guide

Visual modules are shortcodes for adding images, timelines, and other visual elements to articles.

## Hero Image Module

Location: [layouts/shortcodes/visual-modules/hero-image.html](mdc:layouts/shortcodes/visual-modules/hero-image.html)

Displays a large featured image with caption and optional credit.

```hugo
{{< visual-modules/hero-image src="https://ik.imagekit.io/appraisily/SEO/article-path/image-name.png" alt="Image description" caption="Image caption text" credit="Photo: Appraisily Studio" width="full" >}}
```

Parameters:
- `src`: Image URL (required)
- `alt`: Alt text for accessibility (default: "Featured image")
- `caption`: Optional caption text
- `credit`: Optional credit line
- `width`: Image width - "full", "wide", or "normal" (default: "full")

## Timeline Module

Location: [layouts/shortcodes/visual-modules/timeline.html](mdc:layouts/shortcodes/visual-modules/timeline.html)

Creates an interactive timeline with chronological events.

```hugo
{{< visual-modules/timeline title="Historical Timeline" theme="alternating" >}}
  {{< visual-modules/timeline-item date="1950s" title="Early Event" >}}
    Description of the event.
  {{< /visual-modules/timeline-item >}}
  
  {{< visual-modules/timeline-item date="1970s" title="Later Event" >}}
    Description of the later event.
  {{< /visual-modules/timeline-item >}}
{{< /visual-modules/timeline >}}
```

Parameters for timeline:
- `title`: Timeline title (default: "Timeline")
- `theme`: Layout style - "default", "left", or "alternating" (default: "default")

Parameters for timeline-item:
- `date`: Time period or date (required)
- `title`: Event title (required)
- `icon`: Optional icon to display in timeline dot

## Image Gallery Module

Location: [layouts/shortcodes/image-gallery.html](mdc:layouts/shortcodes/image-gallery.html)

Creates a responsive image gallery.

```hugo
{{< image-gallery >}}
  {{< figure src="https://ik.imagekit.io/appraisily/SEO/article-path/image-1.png" title="Image 1 Title" >}}
  {{< figure src="https://ik.imagekit.io/appraisily/SEO/article-path/image-2.png" title="Image 2 Title" >}}
{{< /image-gallery >}}
```

Parameters for figure:
- `src`: Image URL (required)
- `title`: Image title for caption (optional)
- `alt`: Alt text for accessibility (defaults to title if not specified)
